# sqltgen output (the system under test) — regenerated by `make generate`
**/rust/**/src/db/
**/go/**/gen/
**/python/**/gen/
**/typescript/**/src/gen/
**/javascript/**/src/gen/
**/java/**/src/main/java/com/example/db/
**/kotlin/**/src/main/kotlin/com/example/db/

# Generated test files — regenerated by orchestrate.py
**/rust/**/runtime_gen.rs
**/go/**/runtime_gen_test.go
**/python/**/test_runtime_gen.py
**/typescript/**/runtime_gen.test.ts
**/javascript/**/runtime_gen.test.js

# Rust build artifacts
**/rust/**/target/

# Node artifacts (lock files are committed for reproducibility)
**/typescript/**/node_modules/
**/javascript/**/node_modules/

# Python cache
**/python/**/__pycache__/
**/python/**/.pytest_cache/

# Java/Kotlin build artifacts and IDE files
**/java/**/target/
**/java/**/.classpath
**/java/**/.project
**/java/**/.settings/
**/kotlin/**/target/
**/kotlin/**/.classpath
**/kotlin/**/.project
**/kotlin/**/.settings/
